  Te7 7 Chiunn<BR>Siann2-su7 Kau3-hoe7 Tui3 Se3-kai3 E5 Thoan5-to7 Sit-pai7? 
  ChhiaN2 khoaN3 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7. Iok-han7 Hok-im 4 chiuN 35 chat, “Lin2 kiam2 bo5 kong2, Iau2 u7 si3-geh8-jit8, chiu7 siu-koah e5 si5 kau3 mah? Goa2 ka7 lin2 kong2, kiah8 bak8 khoaN3 hng5, i2-keng sek8, thang koah lah.” Goa2 e5 peng5-iu2, goa2 thak8 kau3 chiah-e5 oe7 e5 si5, goa2 e5 sim chiu7 jiat8 khi2-lai5. Chit-e5 Seng3-keng chat sit8-chai7 chin sek-hap8 ti7 kin-a2-jit8. 
  Tui3 Ia5-sou ka7 lan2 kong2, Tioh8 chiong hok-im thoan5 kau3 choan5 se3-kai3, i2-lai5 i2-keng beh koe3 2000 ni5 lah, chong2-si7 iau2 u7 2000 e5 bin5-chok8 m7-bat thiaN tioh8 hok-im. Koh u7 kui2-na7 pah-ban7 lang5 chhin-chhiuN7 Tiong-kok, In3-tou7 teng2-teng2 e5 kok-ka iu5-goan5 u7 chin choe7 lang5 iau2 boe7 thiaN-tioh8 hok-im. U7 ou-bin7 lang5, ng5-bin7 lang5, chhiah-sek lang5----iau2 u7 chin choe7 boe7 bat thiaN Ki-tok e5 mia5. Chi3-chio2 ti7 se3-kan 30 ek e5 jin5-khau2 e5 tiong-kan, 100 hun chi 65 e5 lang5 iau2-boe7 chiap-siu7 hok-im. 
  Siong7-te3 m7 na7 beng7-leng7, I u7 toa7 koan5-leng5. Sou2-i2 lan2 thang oa2-kho3 Siong7-te3 e5 toa7 leng5-lek8 khi3 choe3. I boe7 kio3 lan2 khi3 choe3 hiah-e5 put-kho2-leng5 e5 su7. Hok-im tek-khak tioh8 thoan5 kau3 ban7-pang.” SiaN2-su7 kau3 hian7-chai7 iau2 boe7 oan5-seng5 nih? 
  Te7 1----In-ui7 u7 hok-im e5 tui3-tek8. 
  Lan2 kin-a2-jit8 u7 tu2-tioh8 chin hiong5-beng2 i2-cheng5 m7-bat u7 e5 tui3-tek8, sou2-i2 u7 si5 lan2 kam2-kak tioh8 kiam2 oe7 iaN5 koe3 in. chia u7 3 hang7 tai7-chi3 lan2 tioh8 kap in tou3-cheng, chiu7-si7 kok-ka chu2-gi7, iN7-kau3, kiong7-san2 chu2-gi7. 
  Kok-ka chu2-gi7 chhut-hian7 ti7 toa7 pou7-hun7 e5 kok-ka. Chit hang7 tui3 soan-kau3-su e5 kang-chok cheng7-ka choe7-choe7 e5 khun3-lan5. I e5 khau2-ho7 si7 “Hui-chiu si7 Hui-chiu lang5 e5, In3-tou7 si7 In3-tou7 lang5 e5, Tiong-kok si7 Tiong-kok lang5 e5.” In koat-teng7 beh koaN2-chhut peh8-bin7 lang5, eng7 giau5-gi5 e5 bak8-chiu khoaN3 goa7-kok-lang5, sim7-chi3 soan-kau3-su ia7 bo5 siu7 hoan-geng5. 
  IN7-kau3 siong5-siong5 si7 hok-im e5 tui3-tek8, tek8-piat8 si7 Hoe5-hoe5-kau3 kap Thian-chu2-kau3, nng7-hang7 long2 bo5 hou7 lang5 u7 chu7-iu5. Thian-chu2-kau3 e5 se3-lek8 khah jiok8 e5 si5, in chiu7 iong5-un2 chu7-iu5. Chong2-si7 in e5 se3-lek8 na7 kiong5 khi2-lai5, in chiu7 piN3-choe3 tok8-chhai5-chia2, Ki-tok-tou5 chiu7 siu7 ap-pek khun3-tiok8, i2-kip sun5-kau3. Thian-chu2-kau3 long2 bo5 tam7-poh8-a2 e5 lin5-bin2, na7 si7 Ki-tok-kau3 si7 i5-it siong-sin3 koh sit8-heng5 chu7-iu5 e5 chong-kau3. 
  Kiong7-san2 chu2-gi7 si7 Sat-tan3 sou2 chhong3-cho7, hoat-beng5, choe3 chan5-jim2 e5 bu2-khi3. I pi2 ki5-thaN sim2-mih8 chu2-gi7 koh khah kin2 hoat-tian2, ia7 tiam3 ti7 mui2 chit8 e5 kok-ka teh kong-kek Ki-tok-kau3. Kiong7-san2 chu2-gi7 teh khoa-khau2 kan-ta ti7 Lam5 Bi2-chiu chiu7 u7 100 ban7 lang5 teh sin3. Chit-e5 siu7 sia5-sin5 sou2 kek-tong7 e5, bo5 sin3 Siong7-te3 e5 un7-tong7, si7 choat8-tui3 put-kho2-leng5 tho3-hiap8 e5. In e5 thih-bou7 toan7-choat8 it-chhe3 kap lai7-bin7, chou2-chi2 thoan5 hok-im. 
  I2-siong7 chit 3 hang7 si7 hok-im e5 tui3-tek8, sui-jian5 u7 chiah-e5 hoan2-tui3, lan2 ia7 tioh8 chin3-cheng5, sun7-than3 Siong7-te3 e5 beng7-leng7. “Goa2 i2-keng hou7 lin2 u7 koan5 thang tah8 choa5 kap giat-a2-thang5, koh iaN5-ke3 tui3-tek8 long2-chong2 e5 khui3-lat8; koat-toan3 bo5 chit8-hang7 oe7 hai7 tioh8 lin2.” (Lou7-ka 10 chiuN 19 chat) Ti7 hok-im e5 lai7-bin7 u7 leng5-lek8, oe7 thang iaN5 koe3 it-chhe3 e5 tui3-tek8, koh chiong hok-im thoan5 kau3 choan5 se3-kai3. “In-ui7 goa2 bo5 liah8 hok-im choe3 kian3-siau3, in-ui7 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 koan5-leng5 beh kiu3 long2-chong2 sin3 e5 lang5.” (Lo5-ma2 1 chiuN 16 chat) 
  Te7 2----In-ui7 lan2 kiong5-tiau kau3-iok8. 
  Goa2 chhim-sin3 kau3-iok8, hak8-hau7 si7 chin su-iau3 e5, in-ui7 lang5 thang tui3 che pou2-chhiong in sou2 khiam3-kheh e5.U7 lang5 si7 thian-chai5, chhin-chhiuN7 Bou7-tek (Moody) Hui-ni2-pok (Philpott) kap Kiap-pho2-che5 Su2-bit8-su (Gipsy Smith), in bo5-lun7 u7 siu7 kau3-iok8 a2 bo5 long2 oe7 seng5-kong. Kin-a2-jit8 u7 lang5 khoaN3 pit8-giap8 cheng3-su choe3 iau3-kin2, tit-tioh8 hak8-ui7 choe3 kong-eng5, chong2-si7 goa2 ia7 chai sui-jian5 u7 hak8-ui7 iau2 u7 lang5 boe7 thang choe3 sim2-mih8. 
  Hoat-lan5-sun (Franson) bat phai3 100 e5 sin e5 soan-kau3-su hou7 Te3 Tek-seng (Hudson Taylor). Hiah-e5 soan-kau3-su si7 bo5 siu7 kau3-iok8 e5, u7 e5 chi2-u7 siu7 chit8 sut-sut-a2 e5 kau3-iok8 na7-tiaN7. 
  Te3 Tek-seng khoaN3 tioh8 in e5 si5, chiu7 sia2 phoe chek-pi7 Hoat-lan5-sun kong2 m7 eng-kai sang3 in lai5. Chong2-si7 2 ni5 au7 i koh-chai3 sia2 phoe ka7 i kong2, i i2-keng u7 khoaN3-kiN3 in e5 kang-chok, in choe3 chin ho2 e5 kang, in-ui7 long2 si7 siu7 Seng3 Sin5 chhiong-moa2 e5 lang5, Siong7-te3 siuN2-su3 khau2-chai5 hou7 in koh su3-hok in e5 tioh8-boa5, i kong2, i ai3 koh khah choe7 chit khoan2 e5 lang5. 
  U7 chit8-pai2 goa2 tui3 chit8 e5 soan-kau3-su e5 chi3-goan7-chia2 kong2: “Li2 tioh8 chin7 li2 e5 sou2 oe7 khi3 siu7 kau3-iok8.” Chong2-si7 goa2 tu5-khi3 hit pai2 i2-goa7 m7-bat koh an2-ni kong2, in-ui7 iau2 u7 koh khah tiong7-iau3 e5 tiau5-kiaN7, u7 si5 kau3-iok8 oe7 chiaN5 choe3 gui5-hiam2-seng3 e5. Choe7-choe7 lang5 ui7-tioh8 beh tit-tioh8 hak8-su7, a2-si7 sek8-su7 e5 hak8-ui7, sin3-giong2 chiu7 leng2-tam7. U7 lang5 su-iau3 kau3-iok8, chong2-si7 u7 lang5 bo5 su-iau3, siu7 kau3-iok8 m7 si7 lang5-lang5 sou2 su-iau3 e5, tak8-lang5 long2 u7 ko3-jin5 tek e5 su7-cheng5. 
  Choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 m7 si7 chit8 e5 lang5 ti7 thau5-nau2 u7 sim2-mih8, si7 tioh8 khoaN3 i e5 sim-lai7 u7 sim2-mih8, chiah u7 sng3-siau3 e5. Sim2-pho2-sun kap Bou7-tek, bo5 siu7 sim2-mih8 kau3-iok8, chong2-si7 iu5-goan5 u7 ki-hoe7 ui7 Siong7-te3 choe3 kang. Choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 si7 tioh8 gian2-kiu3 Seng3-keng, ki5-thaN it-chhe3 e5 si5, si7 te7 2 iau3-kin2 e5, I m7 ai3 lan2 sit-loh8 thoan5-to7 e5 iN7-siong7. 
  Siong7-te3 beh eng7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 in2-chhoa7 kap chi2-to7, lai5 kau3-iok8 lang5. Chong2-si7 I iu5-goan5 beh eng7 bo5 siu7 kau3-iok8 a2-si7 siu7 chit8 sut-a2 kau3-iok8 e5 lang5. Toa7-pou7-hun7 e5 thoan5-the2 long2 kui-teng7, u7 siu7 koe3 ko-teng2 kau3-iok8, keng-koe3 3 ni5 e5 Seng3-keng kho3-theng5 e5 kau3-iok8, koh u7 chit8 ni5 e5 sit8-che3 kang-chok, chiah u7 sek-hap8 ti7 choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kang. Goa2 siuN7 che siuN7-hoat put-ko3 si7 hak8-hau7 hong-bin7 e5 siuN7-hoat, na7 bo5 tong-jian5 i tioh8 ai3 ti7 bou2 chit8 hong-bin7 khah u7 choan-bun5-tek chiah oe7 eng7-tit. Chong2-si7 sit8-che3 siong7 u7 chin choe7 bo5 siu7 ko-teng2 kau3-iok8 e5 lang5, iu5-goan5 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 tiong7-iong7 i. 
  Tng5 si5-ki5 siu7 kau3-iok8, tui3 thoan5 hok-im e5 jiat8-cheng5 u7 chin toa7 e5 sun2-sit, chin choe7 jiat8-sim ai3 khi3 thoan5-to7 kiu3 leng5-hun5 e5 lang5, ti7 hak8-iN7 a2-si7 Sin5-hak8-iN7 e5 ho2 khoan5-keng2 tiong sit-loh8 in e5 iN7-siong7. Chit8 e5 kang-lang5, keng-koe3 7, 8 geh8-jit8 e5 gian2-kiu3, u7 4, 5 hang7 e5 sit8-che3 keng-giam7 chiu7 i2-keng oe7 jiat8-sim ui7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 choe3-kang. Mui2-ni5 he7-thiN it-teng7 tioh8 chiong sou2 hak8-sip8 e5 eng3-iong7 ti7 sit8-che3 kang-chok chiah ho2. M7-thang kan-ta chiaN5 choe3 hak8-seng, tioh8 si5-siong5 u7 chek-kek8-tek e5 hok8-bu7 chiah ho2, tioh8 eng3-iong7 it-chhe3 e5 kho3-theng5 lai5 ko3-jin5 pou3-to7, kian3-cheng3, a2-si7 kang2-to7, chin7-lat8 ui7 Chu2 choe3-kang. Na7 bo5 oe7 sit-loh8 khi2-thau5 e5 thiaN3, hoe2-jiat8 e5 sim oe7 siau-biat8, kiu3-leng5 e5 jiat8-cheng5 ia7 oe7 siau-bo5 khi3. 
  Choe7-choe7 hak8-seng pit-giap8, nia2 cheng3-su, tit-tioh8 hak8-su7 ui7 e5 si5, long2 teh siuN7 in e5 hak8-giap8 kiat-sok lah. Chong2-si7 goa2 ai3 kong2, hit si5 si7 tu2-tu2 khai-si2 e5 si5-chun7. In-ui7 hak8-hau7 si7 chi2-u7 teh ka3 lang5 tioh8 gian2-kiu3, i2-au7 in tioh8 kau3-iok8 ka-ki7, an2-ni chiu7 thang tit-tioh8 pi2 ti7 hak8-hau7 sou2 hak8-sip8 koh khah choe7, ia7 bu5-kiong5-chin7. Hian7-si5 in thang choan-bun5 hoa3, thang soan2-tek ka-ki7 sou2 ai3 thak8 e5, jian5-au7 ti7 kang-chok hoan7-ui5 lai5 chaiN5 choe3 koan5-ui-chia2. 
  Chong2-si7 ia7 u7 m7-bat khi3 hak8-hau7 thak8 chheh e5 lang5, chiaN5 choe3 chhut-mia5 e5 leng2-to7-chia2, chhin-chhiuN7 Kiat-pho-che Su2-bit8-su, i lian5 tam7-poh8 kau3-iok8 to7 bo5, na7 si7 i ka-ki7 hak8-sip8, thak8 kap sia2. Li2 bat thiaN-tioh8 i teh kong2-oe7 mah? Li2 u7 chu3-i3 i sou2 kong2 e5 Eng-gu2 si7 long2 bo5 chho3-gou7 mah? Goa2 ti7 pun2-kok e5 si5 chit8-pai2 koh hit-pai2 u7 thiaN-koe3 i kong2 oe7, m7-bat chit8 pai2 thiaN-kiN3 i ti7 bun5-hoat-siong7 u7 chho3-gou7. chong2-si7 chin choe7 tit-tioh8 hak8-su7 a2-si7 Sin5-hak8 Phok-su7 hak8-ui7 e5 lang5, in sui-jian5 siu7 koe3 hiah nih8 koan5 e5 kau3-iok8, iu5-goan5 siong5-siong5 m7-tioh8. Soan-kau3-su m7 si7 jin5-ui5 e5, si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 cho3 chhut e5, Siong7-te3 khoaN3 i u7 sek-hap8 si7 pi2 chun2-pi7 koh khah iau3-kin2. I ka-ki7 oe7 thang koat-teng7 ti7 ta2-loh8 chit8 hong-bin7 pi2-kau3 u7 hah8-eng7. 
  U7 chin choe7 chin ho2 e5 lang5, in-ui7 bo5 tit-tioh8 hak8-iN7 pit-giap8 e5 chu-keh, sou2-i2 boe7 thang jip8 Sin5-hak8-iN7, boe7 thang ti7 kau3-hoe7 kang-chok. Chong2-si7 chit8 e5 lang5 siu7 Siong7-te3 e5 keng2-tiau3 khi3 thoan5 hok-im, m7-bian2 siu7 hak8-bun7 e5 han7-che3. Siat-su2 na7 it-teng7 tioh8 oe7 hiau2 Hi-liap8-gu2 a2-si7 Hi-pek-lai5-gu2, an2-ni chiu7 bo5 lang5 oe7-thang khi3 thoan5 to7-li2. 
  Ui7-tioh8 an2-ni, Seng3-keng hak8-iN7 chiu7 san2-seng, u7 e5 tui3 long5-tiuN5 siu7 keng2-tiau3 lai5 hun3-lian7 ui7 Chu2 kang-chok, Koh chit8 hang7 chiu7-si7 kau3-phai3 koan-liam7, teh ui5-chhiuN5, kui-teng7 chin koan5 e5 hak8-hun che3-tou7, lai5 sit-loh8 choe7-choe7 chin ho2 koh jiat8-sim e5 kang-chok jin5-oan5. Chong2 u7 2 tiam2 si7 ui7 Chu2 choe3 kang e5, choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 chu-keh, chit8 hang7 chiu7-si7 Seng3-keng e5 choan5-pou7 ti3-sek koh chit8-hang7 si7 beh chaiN2-iuN7 su2-iong7 Seng3-keng. 
  Choe7-choe7 hak8-hau7 long2 bo5 ka3 hak8-seng tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 kang-chok, chi2-u7 koan3 thau5-nau2 e5 ti3-sek, ia7 bo5 ka3-si7 hak8-seng tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 sit8-che3-siong7 lai5 eng3-iong7. 
  Pou3-to7-hoe7, ti7 goa7-kok su-iau3, kap pun2-kok chit8-iuN7. Su7-sit8-siong7 goa7-kok si7 koh khah su-iau3, na7 an2-ni choe3, siu-seng5 it-teng7 oe7 koh khah choe7, tek8-piat8 ti7 se3-kai3 e5 kok toa7 tou-chhi7 lai5 ku2-heng5 e5 si5, oe7-thang tit-tioh8 koh khah toa7 e5 hau7-ko2. Goa2 ti7 Ho5-siok8 Tang In3-tou7 e5 si5, hia e5 soan-kau3-su bo5 ai3 goa2 ti7 pou3-to7-hoe7 tiong kong-khai chhiaN2 lang5 koat-chi3. Su7-sit8-siong goa2 e5 hoan-ek8 ka7 goa2 ku7-choat8 chit-e5 su7, chong2-si7 goa2 chiu7 chin3-heng5. Siong7-te3 iu5-goan5 choe3 ki5-biau7 e5 kang-chok, tui3 hit-tiap8 i2-au7, in chiu7 chan3-seng5 goa2 e5 choe3-hoat. Tai7-chiong3 pou3-to7 ti7 goa7-kok si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 beh eng7, choe3 iu2-hau7 e5 hong-hoat. 
  Te7 3----In-ui7 choe7-choe7 sou2-chai7 koaiN-mng5. 
  Sui-jian5 u7 choe7-choe7 thoan5 to7-li2 e5 mng5, i2-keng koaiN khi2-lai5, iau2 u7 khui teh e5 sou2-chai7, siaN2-su7 lan2 iau2 m7 jip8-khi3? SiaN2-su7 m7 eng7 khah choe7 e5 si5-kan ui7-tioh8 hiah-e5 koaiN teh e5 mng5 ki5-to2? Li2 oe7 ki3-tit Po2-lo5 chit8 pai2 koh chit8 pai2 li7-khui koaiN teh e5 mng5, ia7 chin3-lip8 hiah-e5 khui teh e5 mng5. Hian7-chai7 tak8 sou2-chai7 e5 mng5 long2 khui teh, beh hou7 lan2 li7-khui hiah-e5 koaiN teh e5 mng5 lai5 jip8, ia7 theng3-hau7 Siong7-te3 khui hiah-e5 koaiN teh e5 mng5 e5 jit8-chi2. I chai lan2 ti7 sim2-mih8 si5, ti7 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7 tioh8 choe3 kang, I oe7 ka7 lan2 ke3-ek8 kau3 chin ho2-se3. 
  Te7 4----Lan2 bo5 phai3 kau3-giah8 e5 soan-kau3-su. 
  Bun7-toe5 si7 kang-lang5 e5 sou3-giah8. Ti7 Tiong-kok e5 chhan5-hng5 toa7 koh khoah, long5-hu long2 tioh8 eng7 chhiu2 khi3 siu-seng5 it-chhe3 e5 ngou2-kok. Chong2-si7 in oe7 long2 siu kau3 liau2, siaN2-su7 neh? In-ui7 mui2 chit8 e5 lam5-lu2 lo2-iu3 chhut-khi3 choe3-kang. In e5 jin5-sou3 choe7, sou2 beh choe3 e5 kang long2 oe7 choe3 oan5. 
  Lan2 e5 Chu2 ia7 u7 chit-khoan2 e5 ke3-ek8, sou2-i2 I kong2: “thang siu-seng5 e5 si7 choe7, choe3-kang e5 si7 chio2, sou2-i2 lin2 tioh8 kiu5 hng5 chu2 pek kang khi3 ka7 I siu-seng5” (Ma2-thai3 9: 37, 38). Siat-su2 lan2 na7 u7 kau3-giah8 e5 kang-lang5, kang chiu7 choe3 oe7 oan5, chong2-si7 lan2 si5-siong5 teh khiam3-kheh kang-lang5. Na7 kap Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 si5-tai7 pi2-kau3, kin-a2-jit8 lan2 e5 jin5-khau2 si7 ke-thiN, chong2-si7 choe3 kang e5 chin chio2. Sou2-i2 lan2 tioh8 ke3-siok8 iau3-kiu5 chheng-lian5 lam5-lu2 chi3-goan7 lai5 choe3 soan-kau3 e5 kang-chok, lan2 su-iau3 koh-khah choe7 e5 kang-lang5. 
  Te7 5----In-ui7 lan2 bo5 oh8 Po2-lo5 e5 hong-hoat. 
  Ti7 The5-mou5-thai3 hou7-su 2 chiuN 2 chat, lan2 oe7 thang khoaN3-kiN3 Po2-lo5 e5 hong-hoat: “Li2 ti7 choe7-choe7 kan-cheng3 e5 lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5 sou2 tui3 goa2 thiaN-kiN3 chiah-e5 su7, tioh8 kau-thok tiong-sin3 e5 lang5, chiong-lai5 kham-tit ka3-si7 pat8 lang5 e5.” Po2-lo5 e5 hong-hoat si7 ka3-si7 pat8-lang5, ia7 kio3 siu7 ka3-si7 e5 lang5 tioh8 koh-chai3 ka3-si7 pat8-lang5; in-ui7 kang-lang5 siu7-hun3 liau2 chhut-khi3 kang-chok, koh khi3 hun3-lian7 pat8 e5 kang-lang5. 
  Kim-jit8 choe3 ho2 e5 hong-hoat si7 khai-pan7 Seng3-keng hak8-iN7, hun3-lian7 hap8-eng7 e5 kang-lang5. In keng-koe3 hun3-lian7 liau2-au7 chiu7 thang chhe-phai3, tui3 ka-ki7 e5 lang5 thoan5 hok-im si7 choe3 ho2 e5 hong-hoat, lan2 bo5 kho2-leng5 kan-taN kho3 goa7-kok soan-kau3-su tui3 choan5 se3-kai3 thoan5 hok-im, in-ui7 lang5-giah8 bo5 kau3-giah8. 
  Li2 oe7 ki3-tit Ia5-sou tai7-seng u7 hun3-lian7 12 e5 hak8-seng, chong2-si7 au7-lai5 u7 hun3-lian7 70 e5. Po2-lo5 bo5 choe3 bok8-su, i hou7 lang5 hoan2-hoe2, ka7 in siat-lip8 tiuN2-lo2 liau2-au7 chiu7 koh khi3 pat8 sou2-chai7. I hou7 pun2 toe7 e5 leng2-to7-chia2 hu7-chek kau3-hoe7, hou7 in ka-ki7 chi-chhi5, in-ui7 si7 oah8 e5, ia7 oah8 e5 tek-khak oe7 tiong2-toa7. 
  Ti7 Su3-tou5 heng5-toan7 19 chiuN 8-10, 18-20 chat, lan2 oe7-thang tit-tioh8 ki5-biau7 e5 bou5-hoan7. Lan2 chiah ti7 te2-te2 e5 2 ni5 ku2, sio2 A-se-a e5 lang5 long2 i2-keng thiaN tioh8 hok-im. Chin choe7 siok8 ti7 sia5-sut8 e5 chheh long2 ti7 cheng3-lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5 eng7 hoe2 sio, hit-si5 sou2 sio e5 chheh, ke3-tat8 kui2 na7 chheng khou, ia7 ti7 hia to7-li2 toa7-toa7 tit-tioh8 heng-ong7. 
